com.ontotext.s4.common

Class ApiObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ontotext.s4.common.ApiObject
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AnnotatedDocument, Annotation, Item

    public class ApiObject
extends java.lang.Object
    Common superclass for all objects that represent API responses that will be parsed from JSON. The Jackson ObjectMapper used by the RestClient is set up to automatically inject the client instance into deserialized objects, allowing them to have their own methods that make further requests to the API.
